{{define "pieAutoAddUsage" -}}
{{if .IsShowUsageHint}}{{template "usage" . }}{{end -}}
***{{.Prefix}}pieAutoAdd -c <#channel> -r <@role> -o <online|all> -i <intervaltime> -a <amount> -c <cycleTimes> -e <aftertime>***
  Add auto pie task
  **-c <#channel>:** Which channel's people can get pie, `this flag can ignore, default current channel`
  **-r <@role>:** Who is the <@role> can get pie
  **-o <online|all>:** Only Pie to online peoples or all peoples `default online`
  **-i <intervaltime>:** <XhYmZs>(X hour Y minute Z second ) how long time to Pie once, `must > 180s default 180s`
    Example: `1h` is one hour, `1h30m` is on hour and 30 minutes
  **-a <amout>**: Must be a number > {{.PieMin}} {{.Symbol}} `default {{.PieMin}}`
  **-c <cycleTimes>:** How many times to Auto Pie, `must be a number > 0, default 10`
  **-e <aftertime>:** How long time to Auto Pie after create task, same as <intervaltime> but `must >= 0 seconds, default 60s`
{{- end}}
